  "body": "If you configure a static peer via `static-node.json` using a DNS name, and that DNS name doesn't resolve you get the following error, and the peer manager fails to start, so you don't peer with anyone.\r\n\r\n```\r\n2020-08-10 02:29:28.7989|ERROR|6|Unable to init the peer manager. System.ArgumentException: archive01.archivenode.io is not a proper IP address nor it can be resolved by DNS.\r\n ---> System.Net.Internals.SocketExceptionFactory+ExtendedSocketException (00000005, 0xFFFDFFFF): Name or service not known\r\n   at System.Net.Dns.InternalGetHostByName(String hostName)\r\n   at System.Net.Dns.GetHostAddresses(String hostNameOrAddress)\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.Enode..ctor(String enodeString)\r\n   --- End of inner exception stack trace ---\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.Enode..ctor(String enodeString)\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.NetworkNode..ctor(String enode)\r\n   at Nethermind.Network.StaticNodes.StaticNodesManager.<>c.<InitAsync>b__12_0(String n)\r\n   at System.Linq.Enumerable.SelectArrayIterator`2.MoveNext()\r\n   at System.Linq.Enumerable.ToDictionary[TSource,TKey,TElement](IEnumerable`1 source, Func`2 keySelector, Func`2 elementSelector, IEqualityComparer`1 comparer)\r\n   at System.Linq.Enumerable.ToDictionary[TSource,TKey,TElement](IEnumerable`1 source, Func`2 keySelector, Func`2 elementSelector)\r\n   at Nethermind.Network.StaticNodes.StaticNodesManager.InitAsync()\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.InitializeNetwork.InitPeer()\r\n2020-08-10 02:29:28.8153|ERROR|11|Unable to start the peer manager. Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.StepDependencyException: PeerManager\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.InitializeNetwork.StartPeer()\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.InitializeNetwork.Initialize(CancellationToken cancellationToken)\r\n2020-08-10 02:29:28.8766|ERROR|9|Error during ethereum runner start System.ArgumentNullException: Value cannot be null. (Parameter 'peerManager')\r\n   at Nethermind.JsonRpc.Modules.Admin.AdminModule..ctor(IBlockTree blockTree, INetworkConfig networkConfig, IPeerManager peerManager, IStaticNodesManager staticNodesManager, IEnode enode, String dataDir)\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.RegisterRpcModules.Execute(CancellationToken cancellationToken)\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.EthereumStepsManager.RunOneRoundOfInitialization(CancellationToken cancellationToken)\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.Steps.EthereumStepsManager.InitializeAll(CancellationToken cancellationToken)\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Ethereum.EthereumRunner.Start(CancellationToken cancellationToken)\r\n```",
